Question: Are the spectators below the field and the people to the right of the batter both staring?

Reference Answer: yes

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n538684.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='field')
IMAGE0=CROP_BELOW(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='spectators')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='batter')
IMAGE2=CROP_RIGHTOF(image=IMAGE1,box=BOX2)
BOX3=LOC(image=IMAGE2,object='people')
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='Are the spectators staring?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE2,question='Are the people staring?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'yes' and {ANSWER1} == 'yes' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
